------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| Step      | Command                                                         |
| ----------| ---------------------------------------------------------------|
| ✅ Build | `docker build -t pradip-web-app .`                              |
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| 🚀 Run   | `docker run -d -p 8080:80 --name web-app pradip-web-app`        |
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| 🔄 Tag   | `docker tag pradip-web-app your-username/pradip-web-app:latest` |
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| 🔐 Login | `docker login`                                                  |
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
| ⬆️ Push  | `docker push your-username/pradip-web-app:latest`               |
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
